{"tid":248940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撒瑪利亞防止自殺會樓上    男子危坐天台企跳","createTime":"2017-05-19T03:13:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-20T12:11:59.000Z","uid":48093,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d4ac24f528825518bd0fdc02c9dd1bc17f791d8f","tid":248940,"uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:13:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170519/large/1495159181_aab2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170519%2Flarge%2F1495159181_aab2.jpg&h=e734fae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【10:40更新】事主被救援人員拉回安全位置<br />\n<br />\n早上9時許，石硤尾白田邨瑞田樓一名中年男子，在天台危坐企圖跳樓。消防員接報到場游說，警方談判專家亦到場協助。其間男事主悲從中來，掉下眼淚，又不斷抽煙，心事重重。<br />\n現場白田邨瑞田樓3樓，正是香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會的寫字樓所在。職員稱，由於要保障求助人的私穩，未能證實事主是否求助人士，但現階段職員正在場協助。"},{"pid":"0fbc9c7c05b4a5a9a08a9175c8f4276c96d35ea2","tid":248940,"uid":60219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:14:16.000Z","msg":"好諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"358204322b29177a7c9f52bdc82c3f433419ce6b","tid":248940,"uid":61582,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"自殺會：你明剃我眼眉啫"},{"pid":"6511f0c88fed7843bedc4a160adac891fa92e59f","tid":248940,"uid":58666,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:24:21.000Z","msg":"好似串鳩佢無撚用咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"807f9ec1b7e94db8606cf1e00402147163a7b0b7","tid":248940,"uid":51720,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03:31:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好諷刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n報道結尾按慣例加埋求助熱線，仲唔係諷刺？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fee997a48089d930a2ff1477df235083faae7b3e","tid":248940,"uid":59014,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-19T03: